  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/25e2636c514932ce008137b9a2650d83.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br><br>By any chance...<br>do you have old memories that have been <br>folded in your heart?<br><br>Memories that are dazzlingly beautiful and poignantly heartbreaking are <br>colored in our hearts over a long period of time <br>and engraved in our hearts under the name of memories.<br><br>[Rainy Day] is <br>a story about those memories.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/bc0cabecbbee61ed970d50bb08a057b8.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br><br><br>[Rainy Day] is a point-and-click storytelling game.<br>[Rainy Day] consists of a total of three chapters, and each chapter is progressed in a way that different narrators tell their own stories.<br>Players will encounter each story through simple mini-games and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/899ff90b1ff5ecd5ae699982f02624bc.poster.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/899ff90b1ff5ecd5ae699982f02624bc.webm?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/899ff90b1ff5ecd5ae699982f02624bc.mp4?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/1db42bf647fcb6459819cfeaa44c2847.poster.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/1db42bf647fcb6459819cfeaa44c2847.webm?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/1db42bf647fcb6459819cfeaa44c2847.mp4?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/3ee8b48737a71b5deb335d527549c278.poster.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/3ee8b48737a71b5deb335d527549c278.webm?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/3ee8b48737a71b5deb335d527549c278.mp4?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/07b14d478579e3d0ba458756db6ec802.poster.avif?t=1682216808\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/07b14d478579e3d0ba458756db6ec802.webm?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375220/extras/07b14d478579e3d0ba458756db6ec802.mp4?t=1682216808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After 3 chapters, one story related to the main character is completed.<br><br>On a rainy day, listen to the sound of rain and go into the memories that have been folded in your heart.",
